_sText:
Yesterday i released my second map. It is called de_trading.
It would give me great pleasure when the map getting pimped at the
lanmaniax homepage. The map is in its final status, and i hope many people will enjoy playing it! The map has 64 spawnpoints, and all stuff, like the overview, custom content and the nav-file are integrated in a single bsp.
I tried to attach importance to a fair gameplay with many different ways.
